infra.name: te0803_3cg_1e
infra.display: TE0803-*-3AE10-R (2GB DDR) (not compatible with def. Trenz carrier). *SPRT PCB: REV04,REV03
infra.description: Zynq UltraScale+ MPSoC TE0803-*-3AE10-A (2GB DDR) Board (form factor 5.2x7.6 cm) with 4x 512 MByte DDR4, speed grade -1 and extended temperature range. *Supported PCB Revisions: REV04,REV03. Board Part is only with minimum PS-Setup. Use for own carrier or simple SDK debugging. User must configure B2B MIOs manually, depending on his carrier board connection. Without user PS configuration only JTAG is possible with this board part file. Attation: 3.3VMIO are not compatible with default Trenz Carrier for this series!
